  stimulus_text = 'The 1985 film *Back to the Future* is one of the most popular and influential movies ever made, but it is not without its flaws. For example, the movie relies on the trope of time travel, which is often used to make a story more exciting. However, the movie’s use of time travel makes it difficult to create a believable story. In the end, the movie is a fun and entertaining adventure, but it is not a perfect film.',
